These scripts are made in order to facilitate
the creation and further administration of
the hosting which works on the base of:
Apache2, PHP5(as mod_fcgi), MYSQL, VSFTPD.

The scripts are worked out and designed for Debian GNU/Linux.

!!!WARNING!!! install.pl is administered for using only on the newly installed system.

install.pl is administered for installation Apache2, PHP5, MySQL, VSFTP,
and bringing some changes into the system namely creating new group secure
into the system and additing "/bin/date" to the file /etc/shells.

adduser.pl is administered for adding new user to virtualhost and ftp.


